:Class jqSliderSimple : MiPageSample
⍝ Control:: _JQ.jqSlider
⍝ Description:: Single and Ranged Sliders

    ∇ Compose;drag
      :Access Public
      Add _.h4'jQuery Slider Widget'
     
      Add _.h6'Default Slider'
      ('Default' '.slide'Add _.jqSlider).On 'slidechange' 'myCallBack' ('newval' '#Default' 'slider' 'value')
     
      Add _.h6'Ranged Slider'
      ('Ranged' '.slide'Add _.jqSlider 0 100 20 40).On 'slidechange' 'myCallBack' ('newval' '#Ranged' 'slider' 'values')
     
      Add¨_.br(_.Button'Update')_.br
     
      '#output'Add _.div
    ∇

    ∇ r←myCallBack
      :Access Public
      r←'#output'Replace _what,' Slider changed to ',⍕Get'newval'
    ∇


:EndClass